 Our story
Our team
Our clients





Our story
Simple. Safe.
We founded Longview so that we could put to work the investment principles we have always followed on behalf of our own families — for clients we care about.
Our goal is to safely increase our clients’ wealth over time. We want them to sleep well and have total peace of mind.
Our strategy starts with keeping things simple and safe. We invest with our eyes on stability and growth over the long term. We believe so strongly in our strategy that we have literally bought into it — everyone at Longview is invested alongside our clients, in the same stocks and in the same weightings.
We also keep our client base small enough to ensure that we can provide consistently excellent service. Whether client or colleague, we build relationships of mutual respect designed to stand the test of time.










