Longview Asset Management, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 24, 2017 1:18 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Longview Asset Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Longview Asset Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm manages equity portfolios for its clients. It invests in public equity markets of the United States. The firm was formerly known as Longview Management Group, LLC. Longview Asset Management is based in Chicago, Illinois.


222 North LaSalle StreetSuite 2000Chicago, IL 60601United States










